data.description: What a find on this well-maintained brick home sitting on just over 1/2 acre with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, a formal living room, a large family room with wood burning fireplace, kitchen with pantry and dining area.  The HVAC and all ducting and vents were replaced approximately 2 years ago.  The metal roof was installed approximately 10 years ago by Scott Cook Roofing; refrigerator is 1 1/2 years old, microwave, dishwasher 8 months old, double ovens approximately 3 years old.  Enjoy the heated and cooled enclosed back porch with two window units that were used for the owner's plants.  There is a large detached double carport at the back of the home to keep your cars covered.  A large workshop with electricity at the back of the lot (the single story side of the shop is 24x30 and the double story side of the shop is 24x38 with approximately 300+/- sf up top accessed from the back of the building) and would make a great place to either work on cars, wood working, etc. Call today before this great value is gone!!
